:"seo_title";s:0:"";s:12:"seo_keywords";s:0:"";s:8:"seo_desc";s:0:"";s:3:"tag";s:0:"";s:4:"attr";s:0:"";s:9:"replydate";s:1:"0";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"0";s:10:"identifier";s:0:"";s:8:"integral";s:1:"0";s:4:"note";s:0:"";s:5:"thumb";b:0;s:7:"content";s:3211:"<p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">《传说：命运王座》的装备材料副本是一个快速获得装备材料的地方，但是每天都有次数限制，我们要怎么获得更多的材料呢？一起来看看小编为您带来的攻略吧！</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(230, 0, 0);font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">传说：命运王座手游材料副本怎么打效率最高：</span></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(230, 0, 0);font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">进入条件：</span></span></strong></p><p><a href="http://www.9game.cn/topic/jueselei/"><span style="text-decoration:underline;"><span style="font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;color: rgb(0, 0, 255)"><span style="font-family:宋体">角色</span></span></span></a><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">等级达到</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;color:rgb(255,136,0);font-size:16px">24<span style="font-family:宋体">级</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。</span></span></p><p><span style="font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">共三个副本，暮色峡谷、冰封雪域、沼泽湿地，分别只能使用对应的力量、敏捷、智力类型英雄。</span><br/></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(230, 0, 0);font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">游戏玩法：</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">进入材料副本后，会刷定时刷出小怪，一共有</span>3<span style="font-family:宋体">波小怪，这时候我们需要把小怪击杀后，方能刷下一波小怪，击杀完</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">3</span><span style="font-family:宋体">波小怪后，会出现关卡</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">BOSS</span><span style="font-family:宋体">，击杀</span><span style="font-family:Calibri">BOSS</span><span style="font-family:宋体">即可通关。并且材料副本有时间限制，因此进入材料副本后我们需要尽快地将每一波小怪击杀，尽可能在限定的时间内拿到最高的奖励。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(230, 0, 0);font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">材料副本刷材料技巧：</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">小怪刷出来后，会自动向英雄靠近并攻击，因此建议站在副本地图的中间，等小怪都走过来后，再使用范围技能进行击杀，这样可以尽可能多地击杀到小怪，同时也不要忘了带上有范围伤害的英雄技能哦！</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">材料副本五个难度等级，角色等级达到相应难度等级后即可开放。等级越高，获得的奖励越丰富。所以大家快快提升英雄等级吧！</span></span></p><p><br/></p>";s:8:"catelist";a:1:{i:586;a:4:{s:7:"cate_id";s:3:"586";s:5:"title";s:6:"活动";s:10:"identifier";s:8:"activity";s:3:"url";s:18:"news/activity.html";}}s:4:"cate";a:4:{s:7:"cate_id";s:3:"586";s:5:"title";s:6:"活动";s:10:"identifier";s:8:"activity";s:3:"url";s:18:"news/activity.html";}s:3:"url";s:9:"1832.html";}i:1831;a:28:{s:2:"id";s:4:"1831";s:9:"parent_id";s:1:"0";s:7:"cate_id";s:3:"586";s:9:"module_id";s:2:"22";s:10:"project_id";s:2:"43";s:7:"site_id";s:1:"1";s:5:"title";s:27:"英雄介绍——美杜莎";s:8:"dateline";s:10:"1502347446";s:4:"sort";s:1:"0";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:6:"hidden";s:1:"0";s:4:"hits";s:3:"580";s:3:"tpl";s:0:"";s:9:"seo_title";s:0:"";s:12:"seo_keywords";s:0:"";s:8:"seo_desc";s:0:"";s:3:"tag";s:0:"";s:4:"attr";s:0:"";s:9:"replydate";s:1:"0";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"0";s:10:"identifier";s:0:"";s:8:"integral";s:1:"0";s:4:"note";s:0:"";s:5:"thumb";b:0;s:7:"content";s:2649:"<p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">英雄介绍：</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">在游戏中，不少玩家已经获得了超强的智力英雄美杜莎，美杜莎作为娜迦族的领袖，不仅拥有美丽的外表，她的作战能力亦是十分优秀。</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">尤其她的大招可以将扇形范围内的敌人石化，在战局中是一个强有力的控制及输出，同时美杜莎本身的普攻就带有分裂效果，因此无论在副本还是</span></span><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">PVP的战斗，都有不凡的成绩。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:宋体;font-size:16px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;font-size: 14px">背景故事：</span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">美杜莎是娜咖族的公主，拥有石化的力量使她成为娜咖族的领导人。美杜莎与哥哥大鱼人总是有意见不和之处，但是根据娜咖族的重女轻男原则，议会总是决定采用美杜莎的意见，就连身为娜咖族亲王的大鱼人在许多决定上也得服从美杜莎。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">万箭齐发：美杜莎向目标射出一阵剑雨，使扇形范围内的敌人受到伤害并减速，持续</span>4s。</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">秘术异蛇：美杜莎放出一条魔法蛇在敌人之间跳跃，造成物理伤害并偷取生命值。抵达最后一个目标后，它会返回美杜莎身边为其恢复生命值。每次跳跃造成的伤害都会增加。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">万蛇护体：美杜莎召唤出一个可以吸收所有伤害的魔法罩，来保护自己。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">魔化石眼：美杜莎向目标发射石化冲击波，使扇形范围内的敌人被石化，持续</span>3s</span></p><p><br/></p>";s:8:"catelist";a:1:{i:586;a:4:{s:7:"cate_id";s:3:"586";s:5:"title";s:6:"活动";s:10:"identifier";s:8:"activity";s:3:"url";s:18:"news/activity.html";}}s:4:"cate";a:4:{s:7:"cate_id";s:3:"586";s:5:"title";s:6:"活动";s:10:"identifier";s:8:"activity";s:3:"url";s:18:"news/activity.html";}s:3:"url";s:9:"1831.html";}i:1826;a:28:{s:2:"id";s:4:"1826";s:9:"parent_id";s:1:"0";s:7:"cate_id";s:3:"586";s:9:"module_id";s:2:"22";s:10:"project_id";s:2:"43";s:7:"site_id";s:1:"1";s:5:"title";s:24:"装备系统必看攻略";s:8:"dateline";s:10:"1502272251";s:4:"sort";s:1:"0";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:6:"hidden";s:1:"0";s:4:"hits";s:3:"517";s:3:"tpl";s:0:"";s:9:"seo_title";s:0:"";s:12:"seo_keywords";s:0:"";s:8:"seo_desc";s:0:"";s:3:"tag";s:0:"";s:4:"attr";s:0:"";s:9:"replydate";s:1:"0";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"0";s:10:"identifier";s:0:"";s:8:"integral";s:1:"0";s:4:"note";s:0:"";s:5:"thumb";b:0;s:7:"content";s:8335:"<h2 style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:35px;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:65px"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">装备升级</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">　</span></strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: normal;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">&nbsp;</span></h2><p><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">点击界面内</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">右侧</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">的装备页签</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">，</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">切换至</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">英雄</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">装备界面。</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">英雄默认有</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px">6件装备。装备可以使用金币进行升级，大家要记得装备等级受英雄等级限制哦，如果提升装备时发现不能继续提升了，那就快快去提升英雄等级吧！</span></p><p><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><h2 style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:35px;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:65px"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">　</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">装备进化</span></span></strong></h2><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">装备</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">的进化</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">可提升英雄</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">战斗力</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">，</span></span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">是非常重要的一个变强途径，当满足</span>6件装备装备等级MAX之后，玩家就可以点击进化，然后就进化到全新的装备了。星级清零，说明装备已经提升到了另一个高度！</span><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px">&nbsp;<span style="font-family:微软雅黑">当然进化是需要消耗一定的材料的，材料可以在副本、关卡等地方获得。</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;padding: 0;line-height: 28px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">英雄等级</span></span></strong></p><p style="margin-top: 0;margin-right: 0;margin-bottom: 0;padding: 0;line-height: 28px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p style=";text-indent: 28px;padding: 0;line-height: 28px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">英雄的等级受到账号角色等级的限制，角色等级越高，英雄的等级上限就越高。英雄等级的提高可以增强该英雄的各项属性，对于战力的影响也是不容小觑！同时英雄等级也限制英雄装备的等级。</span></span></p><p style=";text-indent: 28px;padding: 0;line-height: 28px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">提升方法：</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">第一</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">：</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">通关普通或者是精英副本，可以获得一定的经验值奖励；第二，完成每日任务，</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">获得经验药水提升等级</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">；第三，完成</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">相应的经验副本</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">，</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">获得经验药水也可用于英雄</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">提升等级。</span></span></p><h2 style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:35px;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:65px"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">&nbsp;</span></strong></h2><h2 style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:35px;margin-left:0;padding:0 0 0 0 ;line-height:65px"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">　</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">英雄进阶</span></span></strong></h2><p style=";text-indent: 28px;padding: 0;line-height: 28px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">英雄到达一定的等级，装备就可以提升到相应的</span>MAX等级并且突破，同时可以提升英雄的等阶。最主要的是装备等级的提升可以大幅度的提高英雄的基本属性值。</span></p><p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">提升方法：玩家花费一定数量的金币，然后通过装备系统中的</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">自动</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">升级系统可以将装备提升到</span>MAX等级，然后再通过消耗一定数量的材料，进化到全新的装备，并且提升6件装备附带的基本属性，提高团队的整体战斗力。</span></p><p><br/></p>";s:8:"catelist";a:1:{i:586;a:4:{s:7:"cate_id";s:3:"586";s:5:"title";s:6:"活动";s:10:"identifier";s:8:"activity";s:3:"url";s:18:"news/activity.html";}}s:4:"cate";a:4:{s:7:"cate_id";s:3:"586";s:5:"title";s:6:"活动";s:10:"identifier";s:8:"activity";s:3:"url";s:18:"news/activity.html";}s:3:"url";s:9:"1826.html";}i:1818;a:28:{s:2:"id";s:4:"1818";s:9:"parent_id";s:1:"0";s:7:"cate_id";s:3:"586";s:9:"module_id";s:2:"22";s:10:"project_id";s:2:"43";s:7:"site_id";s:1:"1";s:5:"title";s:48:"《传说：命运王座》钻石拿到你手软";s:8:"dateline";s:10:"1499593129";s:4:"sort";s:1:"0";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:6:"hidden";s:1:"0";s:4:"hits";s:3:"444";s:3:"tpl";s:0:"";s:9:"seo_title";s:0:"";s:12:"seo_keywords";s:25:"传说 命运 王座 dota";s:8:"seo_desc";s:0:"";s:3:"tag";s:0:"";s:4:"attr";s:0:"";s:9:"replydate";s:1:"0";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"0";s:10:"identifier";s:0:"";s:8:"integral";s:1:"0";s:4:"note";s:0:"";s:5:"thumb";b:0;s:7:"content";s:4091:"<p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">相信玩家在游戏中注意到了，</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;color:rgb(255,136,0);font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">悬赏任务可带来大量的金币和钻石</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。今天为大家带来悬赏任务的攻略玩法，希望能给大家带来帮助！</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">《传说：命运王座》开放的悬赏任务，能让你轻松赚取大量奖励。那么，如何在最短时间内获得更多奖励呢？现在就让我们一起来看看吧。</span></span></p><p style="margin-left:0;text-indent:0;text-align:center"></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(230, 0, 0);font-size: 16px">1<span style="font-family:宋体">：任务模式</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">悬赏玩法是通过在日常活动中，完成悬赏任务来获得丰厚回报的任务，是我们每天赚取银两的必要途径。悬赏任务属于全天开放的活动之一，我们可以通过</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;color:rgb(255,136,0);font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">击杀指定怪或与指定</span>NPC<span style="font-family:宋体">进行对话、完成事件等任务</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">模式完成，完成之后便可以直接在悬赏界面当中领取奖励。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(230, 0, 0);font-size: 16px">2<span style="font-family:宋体">：提升任务品质</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">任务的品质分为五个星级</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;color:rgb(255,136,0);font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">，不同星级任务会为我们带来</span>1-5<span style="font-family:宋体">数量不等的悬赏令奖励</span></span><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">。如果玩家不满意任务星级的话，我们可以选择用使用元宝一键刷新，每日有一次免费刷新机会。随后可使用元宝刷新。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(230, 0, 0);font-size: 16px">3<span style="font-family:宋体">：提升任务效率</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">我们可以上线后第一时间先将任务接下，接到任务之后，我们可以选择等待一定的时间以便和其他任务重叠节约时间，或者直接去杀指定数量的怪物。个人建议大家可以同时去做一些别的活动，这样我们就能同时推进两个任务的进度，大大的节约了我们的任务时间。</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(230, 0, 0);font-size: 16px">4<span style="font-family:宋体">：快速完成</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">倘若认为直接做悬赏任务很耗费时间，我们可以尝试快速完成方法，来进行悬赏任务。我们可以消耗一定的钻石使用立即完成，同时记得要将品质刷新到高品质！</span></span></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: Calibri;color: rgb(230, 0, 0);font-size: 16px">5<span style="font-family:宋体">：获取奖励</span></span></strong></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:16px"><span style="font-family:宋体">完成之后便可以获得大量金币、钻石、经验药水，对于个人英雄培养可是有大大的益处！玩家们千万不要错过了哦！</span></span></p><p><span style=";font-family:Calibri;font-size:14px">&nbsp;</span></p><p><br/></p>";s:8:"catelist";a:1:{i:586;a:4:{s:7:"cate_id";s:3:"586";s:5:"title";s:6:"活动";s:10:"identifier";s:8:"activity";s:3:"url";s:18:"news/activity.html";}}s:4:"cate";a:4:{s:7:"cate_id";s:3:"586";s:5:"title";s:6:"活动";s:10:"identifier";s:8:"activity";s:3:"url";s:18:"news/activity.html";}s:3:"url";s:9:"1818.html";}i:1820;a:28:{s:2:"id";s:4:"1820";s:9:"parent_id";s:1:"0";s:7:"cate_id";s:3:"586";s:9:"module_id";s:2:"22";s:10:"project_id";s:2:"43";s:7:"site_id";s:1:"1";s:5:"title";s:51:"《传说：命运王座》删档测试活动一览";s:8:"dateline";s:10:"1494322818";s:4:"sort";s:1:"0";s:6:"status";s:1:"1";s:6:"hidden";s:1:"0";s:4:"hits";s:3:"566";s:3:"tpl";s:0:"";s:9:"seo_title";s:0:"";s:12:"seo_keywords";s:0:"";s:8:"seo_desc";s:0:"";s:3:"tag";s:0:"";s:4:"attr";s:0:"";s:9:"replydate";s:1:"0";s:7:"user_id";s:1:"0";s:10:"identifier";s:0:"";s:8:"integral";s:1:"0";s:4:"note";s:0:"";s:5:"thumb";b:0;s:7:"content";s:4936:"<p></p><p style="text-align:center"><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 21px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">《传说：命运王座》删档测试活动一览</span></span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;font-size: 21px">&nbsp;</span></strong></p><p><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(230, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">活动</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(230, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">一：</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(230, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">每日签到</span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(230, 0, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">奖励</span></s